Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE HOPE IN THE FLAMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're screwed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good.\NEven if I keep holding the flames off,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my stamina won't last!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That said, my hands are full as it is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess this is it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I went and jumped in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like... this is... the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourselves Disciples of Aban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For you two to die in a place like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and still call yourselves that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You would disappoint Aban\Nin the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Disciples of Aban\Nthat I gave my life to trying to defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,had the most dauntless of souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They were warriors of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A will of iron that\Nnever gives up until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that supposed to be the greatest\Nweapon of a Disciple of Aban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The bastard!\NHe's the one who killed Master Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he said exactly what Master would say!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I fought the Disciples of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me a clown\Nwho lost to a bunch of posers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our enemy is lecturing us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having fought us, Hadorra understands\Nwhat it means to be Disciples of Aban...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}more than we do ourselves!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,\Nwho cares if we can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll resist until the very, very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay. Now what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't change the fact\Nthat we're out of options!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... There one last way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A way out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you can still cast spells, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know about my aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, my Magic Power isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to aim at anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to cast one spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast Rura right there, and fly out above!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do that,\NI'll hit that wall of flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky will be visible when you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to my Medoroa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Medoroa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It can blow everything away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This trap works by focusing\Neight flames in one point!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:06:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That means, if I cast Medoroa above\Nwhere the flames have gathered...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it should disperse them,\Nleaving the sky visible for an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bet on that instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! Use Rura to fly up\Nwhen you see the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll grab onto you immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Casting Medoroa is probably going to\Ndrain me of all my Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's our best option.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a way, try it before you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed to be a corpse soon anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you two make it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to make our last attempt!\NPray for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! If I weaken my Ice-type magic\Neven a little, I'll be overpowered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good!\NI can't cast Medoroa like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With his Magic Power...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore me! I'm doing what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your chance! Cast your spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave my life for this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let Kilban's trap spoil it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If my fight, if the fight\Nof my companions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,end without any victors,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there'll be no one\Nto tell the world about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This corpse has risen!\NConsider it a stroke of luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Medoroa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It opened!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:11:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought it would end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... see the future... with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nine of Diamonds\Nis in its final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to say goodbye,\Nlittle Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Help... Somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this final moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything focuses at the center diamond\Nand vanishes to the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even ash is left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like fireworks,\NI love how sentimental it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a good mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,considering one of them escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more Kill Traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have as many traps as cards\Nscattered all over Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we're lucky we got that brat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold him in high regard for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't underestimate humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of growth potential,\NPopp's is greater than Dai's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,None of them will ever reach this place.\NI'll take care of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One by one, little by little. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To the end of Popp. Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you enjoy\Nfutile resistance as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up! Stand up and try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of Magic Power and stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I managed to save Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You little fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't hesitated...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you would have made it out as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I froze when I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In that moment, seeing you\Ndesperately try to help us survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't feel like a stranger anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't make it either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just couldn't... leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, just look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You fought for your honor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You worked with your companions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You worked hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To fight us fair and square,\Nyou desperately...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you desperately did all you could!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you any different from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you crumble in that instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I reached out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... I couldn't grab Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To end up dying\Ntrying to save my mortal enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban's might scold me\Nin the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. He wouldn't scold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp... I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To give your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,for someone like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't been here,\NI couldn't have cast Medoroa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tears are evaporating instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty shabby place to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's go together!\NMaster Aban's waiting in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}God!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}God of humans!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a Darkling, this is my first prayer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If indeed you truly have the power\Nto preside over the lives of humans...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}save him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Save this magnificent man!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't let him die\Nfor a monster like me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the grand finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn away, you filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have you going to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you had,\NI wouldn't have been waiting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must be dreaming!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is this really the afterlife?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to wait a moment\Nto be healed, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that I owe you\Na word of gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Are you really Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised. I never thought\Nyou of all people would save my student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hadorra I knew would\Nnever have done such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that you are\Nno longer the same man
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that I once knew you to be,\NDark Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's strange saying this\Nto someone I've fought again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you intend to say, "thank you"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're soft! You're as soft as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be meddling again this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,damn Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn Kilban...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that truly was the last of my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me, Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King Ban is a dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget any mercy. Be cold as ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that your students will need\Nfor the battle ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They were glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those students of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So much so... they even...\Nchanged who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,With your power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,lead them... to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,how you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,show your gratitude to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the god of you humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has a sense of poetic irony.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In return for my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,your god brought back\Nthe treasure I once stole...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and returned it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your god let me die...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in the arms... of this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In your last moments, you were one of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}our friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was Aban who saved Popp and Hadorra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was believed to have died\Nprotecting Dai and Popp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from Dark Commander Hadorra,\Nbut with his return,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Disciples of Aban\Nare both bewildered and overjoyed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together with the greatest possible ally,\Nthe party heads to Ban's palace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Return of the Great Hero"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
